        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2285",
        "content": "He had given the word among his friends-and they were many and influential-that here was something which they ought to attend, and, as a consequence, the sale of tickets by mr Quincel, acting for the lodge, had been large.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
