        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2285",
        "content": "At times she wished that she had never gone into the affair; at others, she trembled lest she should be paralysed with fear and stand white and gasping, not knowing what to say and spoiling the entire performance.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
