        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2285",
        "content": "The flare of the gas jets, the open trunks, suggestive of travel and display, the scattered contents of the make-up box-rouge, pearl powder, whiting, burnt cork, India ink, pencils for the eyelids, wigs, scissors, looking glasses, drapery-in short, all the nameless paraphernalia of disguise, have a remarkable atmosphere of their own.",
